Span.Text: "Microsoft Dynamics CRM has given us an eye-opening amount of visibility into our post-sales support processes, and the opportunities that exist to increase the value to the business. We ended up getting a lot more than we expected."
Paul Moisy, Technical Services Manager, Thorlux Lighting
Click to view full case study
Through integration with its familiar Office and BI tools, Microsoft offers customers powerful data visualizations to gain insights on all their structured and unstructured data.

Comprehensive business intelligence and high performance computing solutions from Microsoft give power and utilities companies near real-time self-service insight into business performance and customer analytics. The Microsoft solutions offer a self-service and familiar platform for end users while IT retains full control over data management and storage. Microsoft solutions are differentiated by low cost, scale, and simplicity of use.

Integrate data across disparate systems and provide easy access so you can use it to drive innovation and business performance. Foster better communications and collaboration by reducing information silos and provide service to traditional energy customers, as well as meeting expectations or requirements of public and regulatory consumers of information.
